{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "heer-root",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Heer\nFull-stack: NestJS + React Native/Expo\nMVP v1.0 — May 2026",
      "x": -60,
      "y": -300,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 100,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "backend-standards",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Backend Standards\n✅ Fetch → Validate → Delete\n✅ No Prisma error codes in response\n✅ Single query with include (no N+1)\n✅ DTO ↔ Service non-null consistency",
      "x": -60,
      "y": -120,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "module-auth",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "wiki/concepts/Fetch-Validate-Delete Pattern.md",
      "x": -460,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 80
    },
    {
      "id": "module-polls",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## polls.service.ts\n✅ close() — fetch+include → validate → close\n✅ delete() — fetch+include → validate → delete\n✅ Single query (no N+1 for group admin check)",
      "x": -460,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "module-trips",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## trips.service.ts\n✅ update() — uses trip.group from findById\n✅ Removed redundant group findUnique\n✅ groupId required in DTO (removed @IsOptional)",
      "x": -60,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "module-auth-dto",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## auth DTOs\n✅ change-password: oldPassword @MinLength(8)\n✅ newPassword @MinLength(8) (matches register)\n✅ Consistent password policy",
      "x": 360,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "module-filter",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## app-exception.filter.ts\n✅ Prisma P2002/P2025/P2003 not in response\n✅ Log server-side only\n✅ Client gets message only",
      "x": 360,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 100,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "mobile-standards",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Mobile Standards\n✅ sessionStorage (not localStorage) for JWT on web\n✅ storeEvents.ts — forEach wrapped in try-catch\n✅ Push notification errors caught",
      "x": -60,
      "y": 440,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "concept-fvd",
